lead_paragraph: Jenson Button is fit to drive in the German Formula One Grand Prix following a visit to hospital for a precautionary check-up after a piece of carbon dust lodged in his eye during practice on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Button Cleared to Race in Germany After Eye Check-Up
